<br>
Here are some tips to turn annoying advertising into good advertising.<br>
<br>
Garage sale style - Offer a few items at good prices and they see what else you have.<br>
<br>
/auction BANK SALE! UNLOADING FAST! Come to XXXX at loc xxxx - Fungi 35K, Lammy 1.5K and MORE!!!<br>
<br>
Beverly Hills Style - Offer high end items at very high prices.  They are rare so only the elite will purchase, yet the rest will window shop.<br>
<br>
/auction LUXURY ITEMS ONLY!  Come to XXXX at loc - Ton Po's Bo Stick of Understanding 400K  Manastone 4,000,000p<br>
<br>
<br>
The trick is getting people to look in your window.<br>
